## ⚡ Quick install

```bash
gh release download ${TAG} --repo ${REPO} --pattern quick.sh --output quick.sh --clobber
chmod +x quick.sh
bash quick.sh install --repo ${REPO} --tag ${TAG}
```

## 🔄 Quick upgrade

```bash
gh release download ${TAG} --repo ${REPO} --pattern quick.sh --output quick.sh --clobber
chmod +x quick.sh
bash quick.sh upgrade --repo ${REPO} --tag ${TAG}
```

`quick.sh` prints the exact protected URLs after a successful run. The Stremio install URL has this form:

```text
https://YOUR_HOSTNAME/YOUR_ADDON_ACCESS_TOKEN/manifest.json
```

The unprefixed `/manifest.json` route is intentionally not the install URL.

